title: Net Demand Deposits, Reporting Member Banks, Federal Reserve System for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1919-1934 (2)--Original Data, 1934-1947 (3)--Original Data, 1946-1953 (4)--Original Data, 1952-1956. Data Reflect Monthly Averages Of Weekly Figures. Data Are For 101 Cities. Source: Annual Reports Of The Federal Reserve Board, 1930, P.99; 1933, P. 185; Banking And Monetary Statistics.

This NBER data series m14078a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
